{"tid":409303,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿傑迪錫：唔愛巴塞？證明你唔愛足球","createTime":"2017-09-22T03:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T12:55:47.000Z","uid":2500,"like":15,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff95cfb1cc59c413c7d1ff54a1c2de3a7d31fc52","tid":409303,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"拿傑迪錫：唔愛巴塞？證明你唔愛足球<br />\n新浪網 2017-09-22 10:00:4<br />\n<br />\n　　根據《世界體育報》報導，巴塞中場拿傑迪錫近日表示：「如果你不喜歡巴塞足球，那說明你不喜歡足球。」<br />\n<br />\n　　拿傑迪錫近日通過The Players&rsquo; Tribune表示：「為巴塞效力是我已完成的夢想，如果你不喜歡巴塞足球的話，那說明你不喜歡足球。」<br />\n<br />\n　　對於自己的妻子，拿傑迪錫表示：「當我認識我的妻子時，我感覺到自己真正擁有了踢球的動力，我的職業生涯也從此提升了一個水平。」<br />\n<br />\n　　對於美斯，拿傑迪錫表示：「我有幸與世界上最好的球員踢球，能夠天天在他身邊踢球是我的榮幸。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/7943290/87/20170922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F7943290%2F87%2F20170922&d=5nRT1hnFGvJdwyXKJ6fV%2BTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=57c08860\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/7943290/87/20170922</a>"},{"pid":"56dede07fb9f5a79f5adfb43b9f46b53c3c1db23","tid":409303,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"最恐怖既係唔知ag有幾愛巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96959a0be5fafff35f66cd9b10226ce127c950d1","tid":409303,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:17:54.000Z","msg":"@我愛疤塞"},{"pid":"1af0286a24ee42e514f2a30cb1652e7ba2e0e2cf","tid":409303,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最恐怖既係唔知ag有幾愛巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我斯疑佢巨龍紋左會章"},{"pid":"e752e69cbd6efdef2b1e45b172a446f3a6e7621f","tid":409303,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"怎樣才算愛足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\